<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting">
  <title>{{orgName}} has been deleted</title>
  <style>
    @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
      .container { width: 100% !important; border-radius: 0 !important; }
      .px { padding-left: 24px !important; padding-right: 24px !important; }
    }
    a { color: #0B1F3A; }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#F4F5F7; font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif; color:#3C4858;">
  <div style="display:none; max-height:0; overflow:hidden; opacity:0; mso-hide:all;">{{orgName}} has been deleted by its owner.</div>

  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#F4F5F7;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 16px;">
        <table role="presentation" class="container" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:600px; width:100%; background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:12px; border:1px solid #E6E8EC;">

          <tr>
            <td class="px" style="padding: 32px 40px 0 40px;">
              <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Rooli" height="32" style="display:block; height:32px; width:auto; border:0; outline:none; text-decoration:none;" />
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td class="px" style="padding: 24px 40px 8px 40px;">
              <h1 style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:22px; line-height:1.3; font-weight:600; color:#0B1F3A;">{{orgName}} has been deleted</h1>
              <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:15px; line-height:1.65; color:#3C4858;">
                Hi {{userName}}, the organization <strong style="color:#0B1F3A;">{{orgName}}</strong> has been deleted by its owner. Your membership and access to its workspaces, content, and connected accounts have been removed.
              </p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:15px; line-height:1.65; color:#3C4858;">
                If this was a mistake, please reach out to the owner directly &mdash; we can't restore organizations on a member's request.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td class="px" style="padding: 8px 40px 8px 40px;">
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#F8F9FB; border:1px solid #E6E8EC; border-radius:8px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 16px 20px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 6px 0; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#0B1F3A;">What happens next</p>
                    <p style="margin:0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#3C4858;">
                      You can keep using Rooli with your other organizations, or create a new one of your own.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td class="px" style="padding: 24px 40px 8px 40px;">
              <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                <tr>
                  <td style="border-radius:8px; background-color:#0B1F3A;">
                    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" target="_blank" style="display:inline-block; padding:13px 28px; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:8px;">
                      Go to dashboard
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td class="px" style="padding: 16px 40px 32px 40px;">
              <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6; color:#7A8599;">
                Questions? Reply to this email or reach us at <a href="mailto:support@rooli.com" style="color:#0B1F3A;">support@rooli.com</a>.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="border-top:1px solid #E6E8EC;"></td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td class="px" style="padding: 24px 40px;">
              <p style="margin:0; font-size:12px; line-height:1.6; color:#7A8599; text-align:center;">
                You received this email because you were a member of {{orgName}} on Rooli.<br>
                &copy; {{year}} Rooli, Inc. All rights reserved.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
